description:
The Wailing is a 2016 South Korean Horror film by Na Hong-jin. It can currently be found on Netflix, and in this review I will tell you why you should watch it, and what makes it important to know about. Check back every week for new reviews on horror media, and retrospectives on older films. Thank you for watching.
